Schedule Update for @event.name
-------------------------------

Hi <% @user.username %>, the schedule for <%= @event.name %> has been updated, for more information go to <% root_url %>

<% unless @sessions.empty? %>
<%= @event.name %> Schedule
  <% @sessions.each do |s| %>
  - <%= s.start.strftime("%a %d %b, %I:%M %P") %>, <%= Selection.find(s.selection_id).movie_name %>  (venue: <%= s.venue %>)
  <% end %>
<% end %>
